text:
Very nice and big playground with shade.
Can play in rain too.
Small park but have many facilities
Finally a town council with brain... Built a shelter over the playground!  At least it provides some shade from the scorching hot sun. ALL PLAYGROUNDS SHOULD HAVE SHADE IN SINGAPORE!
Has a tree like play structure and vast area with exercise equipments. Kids can spent quality time
Got playground, fitness equipment, and walking track.
